data.description:
Our 1850KP Series has three bedrooms and two bathrooms with 1,860 square feet of living space. Upon entering, note 10-foot ceilings in the entry, kitchen, living area and master bedroom. The open concept design and corner fireplace in the living area allow for enhanced family time. Take pleasure in his and hers vanities in the master bathroom and a spacious walk in closet that connects to the utility room, making laundry easier. 

Taxes subject to change based on new construction.
